Rage moved slowly while sand shifted under her feet, the weather in this 
place being almost unbearable.
She was in the desert, since the forest life wasn't for her anymore because 
of the metal things that kept shooting her every time she tried to get 
anything to eat.
The tip of her nose was even black because of the frostbite from that metal 
thing that shot her with ice.
Her other wounds were healing nicely.
But she was still hungry and was on the trail now of whatever two things 
belonged to the tracks in the sand that she was following. (rion & diana)
The trail was fresh and she was keeping good time, she'd be on them soon.
